{"tid":2383114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"牛奶公司網絡遭黑客入侵致宜家停業　專家指「潛到好深」料部署逾一年","createTime":"2021-01-27T16:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T08:29:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":298,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"78cce00c142eb60ab1948ec083ddc80aa9dfbda5","tid":2383114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"牛奶公司日前疑遭黑客組織入侵網絡，有資訊科技網站報道指該公司文件被封鎖、電郵被盜用。有資訊科技專家看過有關截圖後指入侵規模大，估計黑客可能已潛伏在該公司網絡一年以上；牛奶公司表示有約2%伺服器受影響，包括日前因收銀系統故障而停業的IKEA宜家家居，但指未有證據顯示客戶資料外洩。<br />\n<br />\n美國資訊科技網站Bleeping Computer引述消息報道，黑客組織REvil約於本月14日以勒索軟件（ransomware）入侵牛奶公司網絡，並將公司電腦等設備上鎖，又稱他們已經控制公司的電郵，聲稱會用以發起「釣魚」攻擊。網站亦發佈兩張截圖，包括被指是牛奶公司內部電腦系統的控制中心視窗，及被指是內部電郵的畫面。電郵內容稱無法存取文件，附上一頁顯示疑為來自黑客的訊息，指所有文件已經被加密，要求對方按步驟登入一個暗網網址。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/PKWUSA7HY5HTHNYDLCTST7KFSA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1G10Q5Itr2k5RrmG8x3kouJNzo5awf6PgG3TcAsmutrRBUDN8zLBMHRUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FPKWUSA7HY5HTHNYDLCTST7KFSA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1G10Q5Itr2k5RrmG8x3kouJNzo5awf6PgG3TcAsmutrRBUDN8zLBMHRUM&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=83921d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FPKWUSA7HY5HTHNYDLCTST7KFSA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1G10Q5Itr2k5RrmG8x3kouJNzo5awf6PgG3TcAsmutrRBUDN8zLBMHRUM&h=cf12c2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/PKWUSA7HY5HTHNYDLCTST7KFSA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1G10Q5Itr2k5RrmG8x3kouJNzo5awf6PgG